        <div class="row gap-4 align-items-center">
            <div class="col-md">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="fw-bold mb-3">Built for iLokishi</h2>
                    <p>In South Africa, thousands of skilled workers wake up every day with talent in their hands but no platform to showcase it. LinkedIn demands degrees. Indeed asks for CVs. Job portals require formal experience.</p>
                    <p>But what about the plumber in Soweto who fixed 100 leaking pipes? The caterer in Khayelitsha who feeds 200 people every weekend? The bricklayer in Tembisa who built an entire extension with just a trowel and determination?</p>
                    <p>Hustle was built for them. We believe your portfolio speaks louder than any certificate. Your reviews matter more than your degree. Your skill is your currency.</p>
                </div>
