<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-5">
        <h2 class="m-0 marker display-5">How this works</h2>
        <p class="m-0 lead text-body-secondary">Find any skill or service you looking for in your kasi with ease.</p>
    </div> 
    <div class="hiw-timeline">
         
        <div class="hiw-step">
            <div class="hiw-step-left">
                <div class="hiw-step-number">1</div>
                <div class="hiw-step-line"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="hiw-step-content">
                <h3 class="hiw-step-title">Create Your Profile</h3>
                <p class="hiw-step-description">Sign up for free and showcase your skills. Add your experience, location, and the services you offer. No formal degree required — your work speaks for itself.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
         
        <div class="hiw-step">
            <div class="hiw-step-left">
                <div class="hiw-step-number">2</div>
                <div class="hiw-step-line"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="hiw-step-content">
                <h3 class="hiw-step-title">Build Your Portfolio</h3>
                <p class="hiw-step-description">Upload photos of your best work. Add before-and-after shots, completed projects, and let your craftsmanship shine. Get verified by the community.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
         
        <div class="hiw-step">
            <div class="hiw-step-left">
                <div class="hiw-step-number">3</div>
                <div class="hiw-step-line"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="hiw-step-content">
                <h3 class="hiw-step-title">Browse Available Jobs</h3>
                <p class="hiw-step-description">Search for jobs in your area by category, budget, or location. Filter jobs that match your skills and availability.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
         
        <div class="hiw-step">
            <div class="hiw-step-left">
                <div class="hiw-step-number">4</div>
                <div class="hiw-step-line"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="hiw-step-content">
                <h3 class="hiw-step-title">Connect & Get Hired</h3>
                <p class="hiw-step-description">Apply to jobs that interest you. Job posters can view your portfolio and reviews. When they choose you, you'll get notified.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
         
        <div class="hiw-step">
            <div class="hiw-step-left">
                <div class="hiw-step-number">5</div>
                <div class="hiw-step-line"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="hiw-step-content">
                <h3 class="hiw-step-title">Complete the Job</h3>
                <p class="hiw-step-description">Do what you do best. After completing the work, the job poster will rate your work and write a review. Build your reputation one job at a time.</p>
            </div>
        </div> 

    </div>
</div>
<div class="bg-body-tertiary py-5">
    <div class="container py-5 text-center">
        <h1 class="display-1 fw-medium">Join us now & Showcase<br /><i>Your Skills</i></h1>
        <p class="lead mb-3 mx-5 text-muted">Join our platform and offer your skills or find skills you might need near you, faster and safely with verified users.</p>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-2">
            <a class="btn btn-dark btn-lg rounded-pill px-5">Get Started</a>
            <a class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-lg rounded-pill px-3">Explore Hustlers</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>